The paper focuses on visual-inertial estimation, which is a key component of robotics systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses multisession mapping, which involves computer vision techniques such as loop closure and batch optimization, making cs.CV (Computer Vision) a likely category as well. The paper also mentions the use of state-of-the-art algorithms, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the system architecture and user interface, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
